	 <section id="section_0540A6C5055540FD826ED7D9CC1120BC">
		<title>Join Marketing Cloud</title> 
		<p>If you see the Join Marketing Cloud button in a solution, your
		  organization has been correctly provisioned, and the solution you are in can be
		  linked to that organization. 
		</p>
		<p> 
		  <image href="graphics/join_mc_button.png"
			id="image_17F1736286334ACAA6A3821D07CEF33E"></image> 
		</p> 
		<p>Clicking this button displays a wizard for you to link accounts. This
		  process 
		  <xref
			href="access.xml#concept_04341546E8B44CDF833F9DDF351A50B9" format="dita"
			scope="local">maps</xref> your solution credentials to your Adobe ID. 
		</p> 
		<p><image href="graphics/join_mc_wizard.png"
		  id="image_34ED31DAF0094D6CA8B2FC340C601DED"><?xm-replace_text Paragraph?></image>
		  
		</p> 
		<note> 
		  <keyword>Adobe Target</keyword> users can be similarly link email and
		  password accounts to the Marketing Cloud. See 
		  <xref
			href="http://microsite.omniture.com/t2/help/en_US/target/admin/t_user_roles.html"
			format="http" scope="external">Set Up Users and Roles</xref> in 
		  <keyword>Target</keyword> Help for more information. 
		</note>
	 </section>
	 <section id="section_2D15D6B7EDF54989A557FF59B4354057">
		<title>Having Trouble - Password Recovery</title>
		<p>If you receive an error when linking accounts, you might need to
		  recover your solution password. Depending on the solution you are using, you
		  may have a different password recovery process.
		</p>
		<p>Generally, to recover a password:
		</p>
		<ol id="ol_EB9B4710BA794FD8B29F05E5B8301882">
		  <li id="li_78466C01057342A89E5C0CA43B774E91">Navigate to your solution
			 login page.
		  </li>
		  <li id="li_A678558F45884CF49A344F345C0D5ECD">Click 
			 <uicontrol>Forgot Password</uicontrol>.
			 <p>For Adobe Analytics users, navigate to 
				<xref href="sc2.omniture.com/password_recovery.html"
				 scope="external">sc2.omniture.com/password_recovery.html</xref>.
			 </p>
		  </li>
		</ol>
		<p>Resetting a solution password should resolve password linking issues
		  for Marketing Cloud account linking.
		</p>
